item.title: Time series Econometrics on the go
item.description: A Shiny app for easy and on the go univariate time series econometrics. No installation required, just upload your data and start forecasting after a few clicks! The models available are: Exponential Smoothing (ETS) model Autoregressive iterated moving average (ARIMA) model Check it out at: https://llucpuigcodina.shinyapps.io/TSEonthego/ and https://github.com/LlucPuigCodina/TSEonthego

item.title: Puzzles and the Behavioural New Keynesian Model
item.description: Herein I conduct similar policy experiments to those of Carlstrom et al.(2012) with a Behavioural New Keynesian (BNK) model, instead of the standard New Keynesian model (only) or a sticky information model. The BNK model does a good job of solving previous issues with the standard model (as already noted by Gabaix). All of this work is already, explicitly or implicitly, in the cited articles, so I wouldnt claim to show anything new.

item.title: Incidencia distributiva del gasto en formacin universitaria en Catalua
item.description: Como afecta, solo en sus efectos ms inmediatos, el gasto en formacin universitaria a la distribucin de renta de los hogares en Catalua? item.title: Determinacy in a New Keynesian Model under a Money Growth Rule
item.description: This note derives the analytical conditions for determinacy in a canonical New Keynesian model under an exogenous path for the growth rate of the money supply. Under cash-when-Im-done timing the model is always determinate while indeterminacy can arise with cash-in-advance timing. FULL TEXT: See in Projects Update: Now you can also find my presentation of the paper at the IV Navarra-Basque Country Macroeconomics Workshop.

item.title: Universitat gratuta, un dret?
item.description: No tenen totes les persones un dret a a leducaci? Tenim dret a rebre una formaci universitria? Existeixen eixes obligacions morals? Em faig aquestes preguntes ja que aquestes sn les realment importants, les de fons, les que determinen la visi del que ha de ser en la societat. Si considerem la formaci universitria un dret, tal com pot ser la llibertat dassociaci, el vot o el dret a socors hi ha bones raons per donar-li subsidis o costejar a travs dimposts la totalitat del seu cost, tal que sigui gratuta per a lusuari.
